      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, so i was just sitting here and i heard this loud pop in my left ear? now it just feels totally blocked like it's clogged or something but i cant hear anything at all out of that side. is it just like tinnitus or maybe just some wax buildup or something? it's kind of annoying but i'm sure it'll go away soon right?",
