    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait so if it's a ruptured eardrum it would hurt like crazy right? mine doesn't really hurt, it just sounds like i'm under water or like there's a big plug in there. so it's probably just wax or some pressure thing? i dont really want to go to a doctor if i can just fix it myself with the oil thing you mentioned. do you think the olive oil will work pretty quick?",
